  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Ekorella!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ekorella is a colorful top-down RPG where plants and animals can be sentient. You and your new friends will explore a fantastic and mysterious world in a surprising journey. Solve puzzles, fight monsters in turn-based battles and interact with unique and lively NPCs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SYNOPSIS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Green is a tomato who moved with his brother to Larandella, a serene city where the oranges live. There, Green meets Palms, Laranje and a bipedal dog called Crimson. However, in one night everything goes wrong, and Green is forced to go on a dangerous and fascinating journey across Ekorella.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/ce22ba9dd1bda3e4aa70f4e0947f1df8.avif?t=1770773257\" width=96 height=143 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ekorella is a turn-based RPG, where you fight strange creatures to gain more power, skills and loot. Grinding is purely optional, and some enemies will require different strategies to defeat. Every party member is important to the team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/7751ed2f46dc12d78fed4ecdf52341e8.avif?t=1770773257\" width=91 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/f4b3dbdce147d7baaffe97a92161e39c.poster.avif?t=1770773257\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/f4b3dbdce147d7baaffe97a92161e39c.webm?t=1770773257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/f4b3dbdce147d7baaffe97a92161e39c.mp4?t=1770773257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ekorella is full of puzzles and secrets to discover. Exploration will be an important part of your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TEAM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alex Rockmaker -Main Dev, Pixel Artist and Writer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leonardo Reis - Game Designer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seni Eller - Composer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YayaCW - Illustrator  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/7325ac2e4bdf757e60e37603ae7462f2.avif?t=1770773257\" width=195 height=107 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Ekorella!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ekorella is a colorful top-down RPG where plants and animals can be sentient. You and your new friends will explore a fantastic and mysterious world in a surprising journey. Solve puzzles, fight monsters in turn-based battles and interact with unique and lively NPCs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SYNOPSIS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Green is a tomato who moved with his brother to Larandella, a serene city where the oranges live. There, Green meets Palms, Laranje and a bipedal dog called Crimson. However, in one night everything goes wrong, and Green is forced to go on a dangerous and fascinating journey across Ekorella.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/ce22ba9dd1bda3e4aa70f4e0947f1df8.avif?t=1770773257\" width=96 height=143 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ekorella is a turn-based RPG, where you fight strange creatures to gain more power, skills and loot. Grinding is purely optional, and some enemies will require different strategies to defeat. Every party member is important to the team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/7751ed2f46dc12d78fed4ecdf52341e8.avif?t=1770773257\" width=91 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/f4b3dbdce147d7baaffe97a92161e39c.poster.avif?t=1770773257\" width=600 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/f4b3dbdce147d7baaffe97a92161e39c.webm?t=1770773257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/f4b3dbdce147d7baaffe97a92161e39c.mp4?t=1770773257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ekorella is full of puzzles and secrets to discover. Exploration will be an important part of your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TEAM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alex Rockmaker -Main Dev, Pixel Artist and Writer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leonardo Reis - Game Designer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seni Eller - Composer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >YayaCW - Illustrator  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387650/extras/7325ac2e4bdf757e60e37603ae7462f2.avif?t=1770773257\" width=195 height=107 /></span></p>",
